headline: 2 Reasons to Like YUM and 1 to Stay Skeptical
summary: Yum! Brands has been treading water for the past six months, recording a small loss of 0.6% while holding steady at $148.81. The stock also fell short of the S&P 500’s 11.9% gain during that period.
